:name:
Fera

:coretxt:
Ability to shapechange.

:cost:
1 Instinct

:req:
Has befriended an feral animal.

:1:
Able to see in dark. This is archieved with abilities that some animals posses

:2:
Able to take shape of an beast. 
Turning fully or partly in any single beast.
No mass is lost in transformation so this may result in giant bat or miniscule horse.

:3:
Ability to turn into several animals. Body size needs to match the total mass.
Each of those still count as part of the body so losing those will result in parts of the body missing.


:tags:
Vampiric
VampiricMysticism
